{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/about/layout,_N_T_/about/page,_N_T_/about"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/about/__PAGE__","/about","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/images/belmont2.jpg\" as=\"image\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/images/belmont-person.jpg\" as=\"image\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/images/belmont-person1.jpg\" as=\"image\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/images/belmont-person2.jpg\" as=\"image\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/356bg-08yr1lc.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/3-5k80pt3ds20.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/15orcrkp-_9ct.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0iec5q4ack_04.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/07u_h6i539_wj.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-3md4xmbj68y2c.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1w58-3y618p4n.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\" async=\"\"></script><title>Belmont Apartments — Refined Urban Living</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Experience luxury apartment living in the heart of the city. Belmont Apartments offers elegant residences with world-class amenities.\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 transition-all duration-500 bg-transparent\"><nav class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 flex items-center justify-between h-20\"><a class=\"font-display text-2xl font-light tracking-wide text-charcoal\" href=\"/\">Belmont</a><ul class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-10\"><li><a class=\"text-xs tracking-widest uppercase font-sans text-warm-gray hover:text-charcoal transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"/rooms\">Residences</a></li><li><a class=\"text-xs tracking-widest uppercase font-sans text-warm-gray hover:text-charcoal transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"/rooms#amenities\">Amenities</a></li><li><a class=\"text-xs tracking-widest uppercase font-sans text-warm-gray hover:text-charcoal transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li><a class=\"text-xs tracking-widest uppercase font-sans text-warm-gray hover:text-charcoal transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li></ul><a class=\"hidden md:inline-block btn-primary text-xs py-2.5 px-6\" href=\"/booking\">Book Now</a><button class=\"md:hidden flex flex-col gap-1.5 p-2\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><span class=\"block w-6 h-px bg-charcoal transition-all \"></span><span class=\"block w-6 h-px bg-charcoal transition-all \"></span><span class=\"block w-6 h-px bg-charcoal transition-all \"></span></button></nav></header><main><section class=\"relative pt-40 pb-0 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 pb-32\"><p class=\"section-label\">About Belmont</p><h1 class=\"font-display text-[clamp(3rem,8vw,8rem)] font-light text-charcoal leading-none mb-12\">A place<br/>to <span class=\"italic\">belong</span></h1></div><div class=\"w-full aspect-[21/9] overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/belmont2.jpg\" alt=\"Belmont building exterior\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div></section><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-32\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-4\"><p class=\"text-xs tracking-superwide uppercase text-gold font-sans mb-6\">The Story</p><p class=\"font-display text-3xl font-light text-charcoal leading-snug\">Born from a belief that Akim Oda deserved a different kind of home.</p></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-7 lg:col-start-6 space-y-6 text-warm-gray font-sans leading-relaxed\"><p>Belmont Apartments was created with one simple vision: to provide a peaceful, comfortable, and welcoming place to stay in the heart of Akim Oda.</p><p>Designed for both short and extended stays, every apartment combines the privacy of home with the convenience of modern hospitality. Each fully self-contained unit features a comfortable bedroom, a modern en-suite bathroom, a fully equipped kitchen, air conditioning, and reliable high-speed WiFi—everything you need for a relaxing stay.</p><p>Surrounded by a serene environment, beautiful gardens, and secure parking, Belmont Apartments offers a calm escape whether you&#x27;re visiting for business, family, or leisure.</p><p>At Belmont Apartments, we believe that great hospitality is found in the little details. From the moment you arrive, our goal is to make you feel comfortable, cared for, and truly at home.</p><p>Welcome to Belmont Apartments, your home away from home in Akim Oda.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-charcoal py-32\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12\"><p class=\"section-label text-gold\">What We Stand For</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-warm-gray/20 mt-12\"><div class=\"bg-charcoal p-12 hover:bg-charcoal/70 transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-4xl font-light text-cream mb-6\">Craft</h3><p class=\"text-warm-gray font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed\">We believe that great architecture requires genuine patience. Every joint, every finish, every threshold has been considered at length.</p></div><div class=\"bg-charcoal p-12 hover:bg-charcoal/70 transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-4xl font-light text-cream mb-6\">Restraint</h3><p class=\"text-warm-gray font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed\">Beauty comes from discipline. We remove rather than add, refine rather than decorate, and trust that simplicity reveals the material&#x27;s true quality.</p></div><div class=\"bg-charcoal p-12 hover:bg-charcoal/70 transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-4xl font-light text-cream mb-6\">Belonging</h3><p class=\"text-warm-gray font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed\">A home is more than shelter. Belmont is designed to build community — between neighbours, between residents and the city, between past and present.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-32\"><p class=\"section-label\">The Team</p><h2 class=\"font-display text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4.5rem)] font-light text-charcoal leading-tight mb-16\">The people behind<br/><span class=\"italic\">the detail</span></h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12\"><div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden mb-6 bg-stone\"><img src=\"/images/belmont-person.jpg\" alt=\"Solomon Agyeman Tenadu\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl text-charcoal font-light\">Solomon Agyeman Tenadu</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-warm-gray font-sans tracking-wide\">Owner</p></div><div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden mb-6 bg-stone\"><img src=\"/images/belmont-person1.jpg\" alt=\"Janet Asabea Kwatiah\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl text-charcoal font-light\">Janet Asabea Kwatiah</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-warm-gray font-sans tracking-wide\">Owner/ Manager</p></div><div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden mb-6 bg-stone\"><img src=\"/images/belmont-person2.jpg\" alt=\"Alliana Okaikai Tenadu\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl text-charcoal font-light\">Alliana Okaikai Tenadu</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-warm-gray font-sans tracking-wide\">Social Media Manager </p></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 text-center px-6\"><p class=\"section-label text-center\">Join us</p><h2 class=\"font-display text-[clamp(2.5rem,6vw,5rem)] font-light text-charcoal mb-8 leading-tight\">Come see Belmont<br/><span class=\"italic\">for yourself</span></h2><div class=\"flex justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap\"><a class=\"btn-primary text-xs\" href=\"/booking\">Book a Tour</a><a class=\"btn-outline text-xs\" href=\"/contact\">Get in Touch</a></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-charcoal text-cream\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-20\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><p class=\"font-display text-4xl font-light mb-6\">Belmont</p><p class=\"text-warm-gray text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs font-sans\">Refined urban living at the intersection of comfort and elegance. A home designed for those who expect more.</p><div class=\"flex gap-4 mt-8\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-warm-gray hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-200\">Instagram</a><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-warm-gray hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-200\">Twitter</a></div></div><div><p class=\"text-xs tracking-superwide uppercase text-gold mb-6\">Explore</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"text-sm text-warm-gray hover:text-cream transition-colors font-sans\" href=\"/rooms\">Residences</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-warm-gray hover:text-cream transition-colors font-sans\" href=\"/rooms#amenities\">Amenities</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-warm-gray hover:text-cream transition-colors font-sans\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-warm-gray hover:text-cream transition-colors font-sans\" href=\"/booking\">Book a Tour</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"text-xs tracking-superwide uppercase text-gold mb-6\">Contact</p><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-sm text-warm-gray font-sans\"><li>12 Belmont Avenue</li><li>Akim Oda, Ghana</li><li class=\"pt-2\"><a href=\"tel:+233244569540\" class=\"hover:text-cream transition-colors\">+233 24 456 9540</a></li><li><a href=\"mailto:stenadu@gmail.com\" class=\"hover:text-cream transition-colors\">stenadu@gmail.com</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-warm-gray/20 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-4 text-xs text-warm-gray font-sans\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Belmont Apartments. All rights reserved.</p><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-cream transition-colors\">Privacy Policy</a><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-cream transition-colors\">Terms of Service</a></div></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3-5k80pt3ds20.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[45678,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1w58-3y618p4n.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1w58-3y618p4n.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1w58-3y618p4n.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[22016,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1w58-3y618p4n.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\nb:I[68027,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1w58-3y618p4n.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/356bg-08yr1lc.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"about\\\"],\\\"q\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"i\\\":false,\\\"f\\\":[[[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"about\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__\\\",{}]}]},\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",16],[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$1\\\",\\\"c\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"link\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"rel\\\":\\\"stylesheet\\\",\\\"href\\\":\\\"/_next/static/chunks/356bg-08yr1lc.css\\\",\\\"precedence\\\":\\\"next\\\",\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"nonce\\\":\\\"$un