 welcoming place to stay in the heart of Akim Oda.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Designed for both short and extended stays, every apartment combines the privacy of home with the convenience of modern hospitality. Each fully self-contained unit features a comfortable bedroom, a modern en-suite bathroom, a fully equipped kitchen, air conditioning, and reliable high-speed WiFi—everything you need for a relaxing stay.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Surrounded by a serene environment, beautiful gardens, and secure parking, Belmont Apartments offers a calm escape whether you're visiting for business, family, or leisure.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"At Belmont Apartments, we believe that great hospitality is found in the little details. From the moment you arrive, our goal is to make you feel comfortable, cared for, and truly at home.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Welcome to Belmont Apartments, your home away from home in Akim Oda.\\\"}]]}]]}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-charcoal py-32\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"section-label text-gold\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"What We Stand For\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-warm-gray/20 mt-12\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"Craft\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-charcoal p-12 hover:bg-charcoal/70 transition-colors\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-display text-4xl font-light text-cream mb-6\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Craft\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-warm-gray font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"We believe that great architecture requires genuine patience. Every joint, every finish, every thr